Parliament, Monday, 03 September 2018 – The Standing Committee on Public Accounts (Scopa) will tomorrow be briefed by the Independent Police Investigative Directorate (IPID) on progress made with respect to high profile investigations. Details of the hearing: Date: Tuesday, 04 September 2018
	Time: 09:30
	Venue: V454, Old Assembly Building, Parliament ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF SCOPA, MR THEMBA GODI. For media enquiries, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Faith Ndenze
